{"tid":1749420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"票站外無得做分流，開聲屌到無優先隊","createTime":"2019-11-24T03:40:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-24T07:18:31.000Z","uid":69277,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"19cbb43f4839c3220fa582d6747fedd66431133c","tid":1749420,"uid":69277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:40:29.000Z","msg":"唔好怕開聲屌呀，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">票站外唔可以做分流，無A至K優先隊</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n頭先係廢老區投票，一開波站內人員已經係站外分隊，分廢老優先隊，仲要行到去隊尾分，話身份證A至K可以排另一條隊，字眼上無講優先，但實際上狂入<br />\n<br />\n流程如下:<br />\n廢老隊-&gt; 啲人好快拎到票 -&gt; 投票區投 -&gt; 主隊無投票區用 -&gt; 再分慢咗 -&gt; 廢老隊係咁入，主隊唔郁<br />\n<br />\n我哋入站內之後，廢老隊至少入咗三/四批，主隊完全唔郁，最後大家忍唔住<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開聲同咗選舉主任講，要求唔做站外分流，如果再做站外分流，會打去選舉事務處投訴</span></span><br />\n<br />\n投完票出嚟，站內站外啲人一齊狂屌，最後成功無咗優先隊<br />\n<br />\n勿相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41c7ee1f86fe15a770dc40810b4c37c571ac0436","tid":1749420,"uid":69277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:40:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"528a8c4abe9cdffa4df9a1829adc3735e007a89b","tid":1749420,"uid":69277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:43:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"327786f3eacd1c6d3a24ea086e6f6aabaa51c9e6","tid":1749420,"uid":69277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n記得開聲屌到無優先分流站<br />\n站外無得做分流</span></span>"},{"pid":"34be3964bf9d95941de5ed2c5de236b5fca28dee","tid":1749420,"uid":42799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"327786f3eacd1c6d3a24ea086e6f6aabaa51c9e6","tid":1749420,"uid":69277,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:43:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n記得開聲屌到無優先分流站<br />\n站外無得做分流</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:44:14.000Z","msg":"今朝已經屌左"},{"pid":"85cd89a7b1d95d5d5bde2bae7ee8029561804247","tid":1749420,"uid":7692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:44:51.000Z","msg":"［投訴熱線］一人一個廢老隊票站<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1749376\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1749376</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n幫手報同投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3ba4fcceb6337a5a4d3ccf2145c1a101875c3e","tid":1749420,"uid":173137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:45:49.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"1bd026874463109f7cb16b7924f136262cfd81d7","tid":1749420,"uid":173137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:45:59.000Z","msg":"推呀！"},{"pid":"395a72cba3f7c1e672dc3849e118a1c784ede4f4","tid":1749420,"uid":173137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:46:10.000Z","msg":"出聲呀！"},{"pid":"3c8bb37f0860202287c2ed3d7e50eb3fd7f6b72c","tid":1749420,"uid":69277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:47:32.000Z","msg":"開頭都諗住一個人屌無用，最後成班街坊一齊屌呀<br />\n<br />\n多你一個真係好多，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">投票無分年齡，無人可以優先投票</span>"},{"pid":"01b37b99ebb05fac054461b0eb574a26bcd62920","tid":1749420,"uid":65042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"推，唔可以比人得逞<br />\n<br />\n第一次投唔熟<br />\n<br />\n比人分開左，條隊唔識郁<br />\n老人隊係咁郁送人入去拎票"},{"pid":"9ef7928625f0694e6e613cdb78b53c9e41a9f1ea","tid":1749420,"uid":69277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01b37b99ebb05fac054461b0eb574a26bcd62920","tid":1749420,"uid":65042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:47:51.000Z","msg":"推，唔可以比人得逞<br />\n<br />\n第一次投唔熟<br />\n<br />\n比人分開左，條隊唔識郁<br />\n老人隊係咁郁送人入去拎票"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"致電選舉事務處 28911001"},{"p